data.description: Don't miss this better than new, gorgeous single story home in the desirable Stonebridge subdivision, Terry Sanford School District. The exterior is freshly painted, PVC fascia boards newly installed so you never have to worry about water damage. The gorgeous hardwood floors are throughout the home. Enjoy the sunroom located off the family room, with beautiful views to the backyard. The primary suite is on the opposite side of the house from the remaining bedrooms, providing privacy for all. The owner's recently expanded the backyard deck and replaced the wood with Trex decking, which also surrounds the above ground pool. The vinyl privacy fence and a large shed are wonderfully maintained. Crawl space was encapsulated, sump pump and dehumidifier added in 2022. There is a transferable termite bond for added peace of mind. You have to see this one!
